pr_title: Create a Latent Dirichlet Allocation model for Deep AQAtik project #696
pr_body:
- Jupyter-notebook for LDA model

- new functions for text preprocessing in preprocess_data.py. The new functions provide removal of stopwords and punctuations, lemmatizaton and a method to extract words from the neighbors of a predefined set of words e.g. ('fail','exception','throw').

- Changes on the folder structure of non-contextual models
